# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok french president nicolas sarkozy arrived in quake-ravaged haiti wednesday to survey the damage wrought by last month 's devastating earthquake , and to assess relief operations .
# ::alignments
(a / arrive-01
      :ARG1 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Nicolas"
                  :op2 "Sarkozy")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (g / government-organization
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "French"))
                  :ARG2 (p2 / president)))
      :ARG4 (c / city
            :name (n3 / name
                  :op1 "Hiti")
            :ARG1-of (r / ravage-01
                  :ARG0 (q / quake)))
      :time (w / wednesday)
      :purpose (a2 / and
            :op1 (s / survey-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (d / damage-01
                        :ARG1-of (w2 / wreak-01
                              :ARG0 (e / earthquake
                                    :time (m / month
                                          :mod (l / last))
                                    :ARG0-of (d2 / devastate-01)))))
            :op2 (a3 / assess-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (o / operate-01
                        :mod (r2 / relieve-01)))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok online auctioneer ebay and internet travel auctioneer priceline announced friday they 're pairing to create new online travel booking service .
# ::alignments
(a / announce-01
      :ARG0 (a2 / and
            :op1 (c / company
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "eBay")
                  :mod (a3 / auction-off-01
                        :medium (o / online)))
            :op2 (c2 / company
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "P priceline")
                  :mod (a4 / auction-off-01
                        :medium (ii / internet))))
      :ARG1 (p / pair-01
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 c2
            :ARG2 (c3 / create-01
                  :ARG0 c2
                  :ARG1 (s / service
                        :ARG0-of (b / book-03
                              :ARG3 (t / travel-01))
                        :ARG1-of (n3 / new-01)
                        :mod (o2 / online))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday)))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the russian state duma or lower house of the parliament released a statement wednesday to express `` serious concern '' over the latest developments in georgia after u. s. army servicemen 's entered the ex-soviet republic .
# ::alignments
(s / state-01
      :ARG0 (o / or
            :op1 (g / government-organization
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "State"
                        :op2 "Duma")
                  :mod (c / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Russia")))
            :op2 (g2 / government-organization
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Lower"
                        :op2 "House")
                  :part-of (g3 / government-organization
                        :name (n4 / name
                              :op1 "Parliament"))))
      :time (w / wednesday)
      :purpose (e / express-01
            :ARG0 o
            :ARG1 (c2 / concern-01
                  :ARG0 (d / develop-02
                        :location (c3 / country
                              :name (n5 / name
                                    :op1 "Georgia"))
                        :time (a / after
                              :op1 (e2 / enter-01
                                    :ARG0 (p / person
                                          :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                                                :ARG1 (m / military
                                                      :name (n6 / name
                                                            :op1 "U.S."
                                                            :op2 "Army"))
                                                :ARG2 (s2 / serviceman)))
                                    :ARG1 (r / republic
                                          :mod (c4 / country
                                                :name (n7 / name
                                                      :op1 "soviet")
                                                :time (e3 / ex))))
                              :mod (l / last)))
                  :ARG1 o
                  :ARG1-of (s3 / serious-02))))

# ::id 4 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

      :ARG0 (t / television

                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Hugo"
                        :op2 "Chavez")

                        :ARG1 (c / country
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Venezuela"))
                        :ARG2 (p2 / president)))
            :ARG1 c
            :name (n3 / name
                  :op1 "Cuba"))
      :ord (o / ordinal-entity
            :value 1
            :range (s2 / since
                  :op1 (p3 / pass-03
                        :ARG1 (p4 / presidency
                              :ARG2 (p5 / person
                                    :name (n4 / name
                                          :op1 "Fidel"
                                          :op2 "Castro"))
                              :ARG3 (p6 / person
                                    :name (n5 / name
                                          :op1 "Raul")
                                    :ARG0-of (h2 / have-rel-role-91
                                          :ARG1 p
                                          :ARG2 (b / brother))
                                    :ARG1-of (h3 / have-degree-91
                                          :ARG2 (y / young)
                                          :ARG3 (m / more))))))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (s3 / saturday))))

                  :op3 "Bush")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG2 (p2 / president)))
      :ARG1 (p3 / pitch
            :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                  :value 1)
            :part-of (g / game
                  :mod (s / series
                        :mod (w / world))
                  :location (s2 / stadium
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Yankee"))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t2 / tuesday)
            :dayperiod (n3 / night))
      :manner (a / aim-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (p4 / project-02
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (a2 / air
                        :mod (n4 / normal-02))
                  :concession (w2 / warn-01
                        :ARG0 (g2 / government-organization
                              :ARG0-of (g3 / govern-01))
                        :ARG1 (a3 / attack-01
                              :mod (t3 / terror)
                              :ARG1-of (n5 / new-01)
                              :ARG1-of (p5 / possible-01))))))
